[Same family]    - integral to integral, float to float

widning        - smaller type to larger type, short --> int
                 fine with Java        
                ex) int e = 3; byte f = e;

narrowing      - larger type to smaller type, double --> float
                not fine with Java  
                ex) int c = 4; long d = 4;


[Different families] 

promotion        -int --> float        double a = 3.47; int b = a;            
                 -Fine with Java  
                 -float a = 3L;

demotion         -float --> long       int g = 4; float h = g;
                 -not fine with Java
                 -Long b = (long)3.4;
